OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780783874
OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,FRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva has
OL,7,Fwon her first Grand Slam title by
OL,8,Fwinning the French Open final.
OL,10,FAndreeva, 19, beat 114th-ranked Polish
OL,11,Fqualifier Maja Chwalinska by 6-3, 6-2
OL,12,Fon Saturday.
OL,14,FIt makes her the youngest player to
OL,15,Fwin the women's singles title since
OL,16,FMonica Seles, who was 18 when she
OL,17,Flanded her third straight French Open
OL,18,Fin 1994.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
