OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"You're so young and talented. It's so
OL,12,Fannoying," Chwalinska, 24, told
OL,13,FAndreeva during the awards ceremony.
OL,15,FChwalinska was attempting to become
OL,16,Fthe first qualifier to capture the
OL,17,FRoland Garros title.
