CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780783874
OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,FWhen Andreeva executed a backhand
OL,7,Fcross-court winner on her first match
OL,8,Fpoint, she released her racket and
OL,9,Fdropped down onto the clay on her
OL,10,Fknees to celebrate as she covered her
OL,11,Fface with her hands.
OL,13,FThe teenager later took the unusual
OL,14,Fstep of thanking herself "for
OL,15,Fbelieving in myself, always giving my
OL,16,F100%, even when it's tough, trying
OL,17,Fevery day to be better as a person and
OL,18,Fas a player, believing that I can do
OL,19,Fthis, fighting so many demons inside
OL,20,Fof me".
OL,26,@vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
