CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780783874
OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,F"Only I know how tough it was for me.
OL,7,FHow nervous I was throughout these two
OL,8,Fweeks," Andreeva said.
OL,10,FAndreeva also thanked her
OL,11,Fpsychologist, who she said was
OL,12,Fwatching from Florida:
OL,14,F"Everything that you've told me I've
OL,15,Fbeen trying to use these two weeks and
OL,16,FI would say that it worked not bad. So
OL,17,Fthank you so much," she said.
OL,19,FAndreeva was born Siberia and moved to
OL,20,FSochi and eventually France to develop
OL,21,Fher tennis career.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
