OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780783874
OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,FShe drew a loud applause from the
OL,7,Fcrowd on Court Philippe-Chatrier when
OL,8,Fshe spoke a few words of French during
OL,9,Fthe trophy presentation.
OL,11,F"Thanks for your support today and
OL,12,Fover these past two marvelous weeks
OL,13,Fhere in Paris. It was very important
OL,14,Ffor me," Andreeva said.
