PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780783874
OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,FAndreeva has been considered a Grand
OL,7,FSlam contender since she burst onto
OL,8,Fthe scene as a 15-year-old at the 2023
OL,9,FMadrid Open, where she became the
OL,10,Fthird youngest player to win a main
OL,11,Fdraw match at a WTA 1000 tournament
OL,12,Fand made the quarterfinals.
OL,14,FLately, she has had to contend with
OL,15,Fplaying under neutral status and
OL,16,Fwithout her country's flag due to the
OL,17,Fwar with Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
