FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780783874
OL,3,CRussian teenager Mirra Andreeva wins
OL,4,CGrand Slam title at French Open
OL,6,FWhen she beat Marta Kostyuk in the
OL,7,Fsemifinals, Kostyuk refused to shake
OL,8,Fher hand, as has been the custom for
OL,9,FUkrainian players facing Russians ever
OL,10,Fsince the war started in 2022.
OL,12,FAndreeva has gone a step further than
OL,13,Fher coach, Conchita Martinez, who lost
OL,14,Fthe 2000 French Open final to Mary
OL,15,FPierce.
OL,17,FAlexander Zverev will play Flavio
OL,18,FCobolli in the men's final on Sunday
OL,19,Fto conclude the wildest Grand Slam in
OL,20,Frecent memory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
